proceedings of the 34th international conference in high energy physics ichep08 proceedings of the 34th international conference in high energy physics ichep08 philadelphia pennsylvania july 29 august 5 2008 slac econf c080730 home proceedings how to cite conference home preface the 34th international conference in high energy physics ichep08 took place from 29 july to 5 august 2008 on the campus of the university of pennsylvania in philadelphia pennsylvania the venue was the perelman quadrangle the registrants included over 700 physicists from 38 countries the conference began with three days of parallel sessions divided into fifteen subject categories over 900 abstracts were submitted to the parallel sessions the parallel sessions were followed by three days of plenary talks the social program included an opening reception a concert a public lecture and a conference dinner at the philadelphia museum of art in total there were 274 parallel talks and 40 plenary talks one particularly successful part of the conference was the poster session which featured 170 posters and facilitated significant participation by young scientists links to these posters as well as the slides of the talks are included in these proceedings slac slac national accelerator menlo park ca operated by stanford university for the us dept of energy
